SELECT [d].[madon], [d].[PhuongThucThanhToan], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang], [t].[madon], [t].[malaptop], [t].[dongia], [t].[gia], [t].[soluong], [t].[malaptop0], [t].[cpu], [t].[giaban], [t].[gpu], [t].[hardware], [t].[hinh], [t].[mahang], [t].[manhinh], [t].[manhucau], [t].[mota], [t].[ngaycapnhat], [t].[pin], [t].[ram], [t].[soluongton], [t].[tenlaptop], [t].[trangthai]
FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[gia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t] ON [d].[madon] = [t].[madon]
WHERE [d].[makh] = @__user_Id_0
ORDER BY [d].[ngaydat] DESC, [d].[madon], [t].[madon], [t].[malaptop]

SELECT TOP(@__p_0) CASE
    WHEN CAST(LEN([l].[tenlaptop]) AS int) > 20 THEN COALESCE(SUBSTRING([l].[tenlaptop], 0 + 1, 20), N'') + N'...'
    ELSE [l].[tenlaptop]
END AS [LaptopName], COALESCE(SUM([c].[soluong]), 0) AS [TotalSold]
FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
GROUP BY [c].[malaptop], [l].[tenlaptop]
ORDER BY COALESCE(SUM([c].[soluong]), 0) DESC

SELECT TOP(@__p_0) CASE
    WHEN CAST(LEN([l].[tenlaptop]) AS int) > 20 THEN COALESCE(SUBSTRING([l].[tenlaptop], 0 + 1, 20), N'') + N'...'
    ELSE [l].[tenlaptop]
END AS [LaptopName], COALESCE(SUM([c].[soluong]), 0) AS [TotalSold]
FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]

FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
WHERE [d].[tinhtrang] = 'COMPLETED' AND [d].[ngaygiao] IS NOT NULL AND CONVERT(date, [d].[ngaygiao]) = CONVERT(date, GETDATE())
2025-01-21 07:02:43.212 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (70ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT TOP(@__p_0) CASE
    WHEN CAST(LEN([l].[tenlaptop]) AS int) > 20 THEN COALESCE(SUBSTRING([l].[tenlaptop], 0 + 1, 20), N'') + N'...'
    ELSE [l].[tenlaptop]
END AS [LaptopName], COALESCE(SUM([c].[soluong]), 0) AS [TotalSold]
FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
GROUP BY [c].[malaptop], [l].[tenlaptop]
ORDER BY COALESCE(SUM([c].[soluong]), 0) DESC

SELECT [d].[madon], [d].[PhuongThucThanhToan], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang], [t].[madon], [t].[malaptop], [t].[dongia], [t].[gia], [t].[soluong], [t].[malaptop0], [t].[cpu], [t].[giaban], [t].[gpu], [t].[hardware], [t].[hinh], [t].[mahang], [t].[manhinh], [t].[manhucau], [t].[mota], [t].[ngaycapnhat], [t].[pin], [t].[ram], [t].[soluongton], [t].[tenlaptop], [t].[trangthai]
FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c1].[madon], [c1].[malaptop], [c1].[dongia], [c1].[gia], [c1].[soluong], [l1].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l1].[cpu], [l1].[giaban], [l1].[gpu], [l1].[hardware], [l1].[hinh], [l1].[mahang], [l1].[manhinh], [l1].[manhucau], [l1].[mota], [l1].[ngaycapnhat], [l1].[pin], [l1].[ram], [l1].[soluongton], [l1].[tenlaptop], [l1].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c1]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l1] ON [c1].[malaptop] = [l1].[malaptop]
) AS [t] ON [d].[madon] = [t].[madon]
WHERE CONVERT(varchar(11), [d].[madon]) LIKE @__searchTerm_0_contains ESCAPE N'\' OR [d].[makh] LIKE @__searchTerm_0_contains_1 ESCAPE N'\' OR EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
    WHERE [d].[madon] = [c].[madon] AND [l].[tenlaptop] LIKE @__searchTerm_0_contains_2 ESCAPE N'\') OR EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l0] ON [c0].[malaptop] = [l0].[malaptop]
    LEFT JOIN [Hang] AS [h] ON [l0].[mahang] = [h].[mahang]
    WHERE [d].[madon] = [c0].[madon] AND [h].[tenhang] LIKE @__searchTerm_0_contains_3 ESCAPE N'\')
ORDER BY [d].[madon], [t].[madon], [t].[malaptop]

SELECT [d].[madon], [d].[PhuongThucThanhToan], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang], [t].[madon], [t].[malaptop], [t].[dongia], [t].[gia], [t].[soluong], [t].[malaptop0], [t].[cpu], [t].[giaban], [t].[gpu], [t].[hardware], [t].[hinh], [t].[mahang], [t].[manhinh], [t].[manhucau], [t].[mota], [t].[ngaycapnhat], [t].[pin], [t].[ram], [t].[soluongton], [t].[tenlaptop], [t].[trangthai]
FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c1].[madon], [c1].[malaptop], [c1].[dongia], [c1].[gia], [c1].[soluong], [l1].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l1].[cpu], [l1].[giaban], [l1].[gpu], [l1].[hardware], [l1].[hinh], [l1].[mahang], [l1].[manhinh], [l1].[manhucau], [l1].[mota], [l1].[ngaycapnhat], [l1].[pin], [l1].[ram], [l1].[soluongton], [l1].[tenlaptop], [l1].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c1]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l1] ON [c1].[malaptop] = [l1].[malaptop]
) AS [t] ON [d].[madon] = [t].[madon]
WHERE CONVERT(varchar(11), [d].[madon]) LIKE @__searchTerm_0_contains ESCAPE N'\' OR [d].[makh] LIKE @__searchTerm_0_contains_1 ESCAPE N'\' OR EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
    WHERE [d].[madon] = [c].[madon] AND [l].[tenlaptop] LIKE @__searchTerm_0_contains_2 ESCAPE N'\') OR EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l0] ON [c0].[malaptop] = [l0].[malaptop]
    LEFT JOIN [Hang] AS [h] ON [l0].[mahang] = [h].[mahang]
    WHERE [d].[madon] = [c0].[madon] AND [h].[tenhang] LIKE @__searchTerm_0_contains_3 ESCAPE N'\')
ORDER BY [d].[madon], [t].[madon], [t].[malaptop]

    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[gia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
) AS [t] ON [d].[madon] = [t].[madon]
ORDER BY [d].[ngaydat] DESC, [d].[madon], [t].[madon], [t].[malaptop]

    WHEN CAST(LEN([l].[tenlaptop]) AS int) > 20 THEN COALESCE(SUBSTRING([l].[tenlaptop], 0 + 1, 20), N'') + N'...'

2025-01-21 08:40:54.392 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (265ms) [Parameters=[@__user_Id_0='?' (Size = 450)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [d].[madon], [d].[PhuongThucThanhToan], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang], [t].[madon], [t].[malaptop], [t].[dongia], [t].[gia], [t].[soluong], [t].[malaptop0], [t].[cpu], [t].[giaban], [t].[gpu], [t].[hardware], [t].[hinh], [t].[mahang], [t].[manhinh], [t].[manhucau], [t].[mota], [t].[ngaycapnhat], [t].[pin], [t].[ram], [t].[soluongton], [t].[tenlaptop], [t].[trangthai]
FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[madon], [c].[malaptop], [c].[dongia], [c].[gia], [c].[soluong], [l].[malaptop] AS [malaptop0], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [d].[madon], [d].[PhuongThucThanhToan], [d].[gia], [d].[giaohang], [d].[makh], [d].[ngaydat], [d].[ngaygiao], [d].[thanhtoan], [d].[tinhtrang]

    WHERE [d].[makh] = @__userId_0 AND [d].[tinhtrang] = 'CART'

    WHEN CAST(LEN([l].[tenlaptop]) AS int) > 20 THEN COALESCE(SUBSTRING([l].[tenlaptop], 0 + 1, 20), N'') + N'...'

SELECT [l].[malaptop], [l].[cpu], [l].[giaban], [l].[gpu], [l].[hardware], [l].[hinh], [l].[mahang], [l].[manhinh], [l].[manhucau], [l].[mota], [l].[ngaycapnhat], [l].[pin], [l].[ram], [l].[soluongton], [l].[tenlaptop], [l].[trangthai], [n].[manhucau], [n].[tennhucau], [h].[mahang], [h].[hinh], [h].[tenhang]
FROM [Laptop] AS [l]

SELECT TOP(@__p_0) CASE
    WHEN CAST(LEN([l].[tenlaptop]) AS int) > 20 THEN COALESCE(SUBSTRING([l].[tenlaptop], 0 + 1, 20), N'') + N'...'
    ELSE [l].[tenlaptop]
END AS [LaptopName], COALESCE(SUM([c].[soluong]), 0) AS [TotalSold]
FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
INNER JOIN [Laptop] AS [l] ON [c].[malaptop] = [l].[malaptop]
GROUP BY [c].[malaptop], [l].[tenlaptop]
ORDER BY COALESCE(SUM([c].[soluong]), 0) DESC
